# AI-Based Lip Reading Communication Device

This project uses computer vision and deep learning to convert lip movements into text and speech.

Technologies:
- OpenCV
- Dlib facial landmarks
- TensorFlow / Keras
- Flask web interface
- ESP32 hardware integration

Pipeline:
Camera → Lip detection → Frame preprocessing → 3D CNN model → Word prediction → Text to speech

Applications:
Assistive communication for non-verbal individuals.
